        :markdown-it(linkify)
            Please, note that `reverse` only applies to the latest step and could not be stacked.
            ```pug
            button(
                data-hz-resource='HzAnim',
                data-opt-hz-anim-on='click',
                data-opt-hz-anim-do={"backgroundColor":"#ff0000"},
                data-opt-hz-anim-do-2=[{"width":"10em","height":"10em"}],
                data-opt-hz-anim-do-3="reverse"
            ) Go and back
            ```
            ```HTML
            <button
                data-hz-resource='HzAnim'
                data-opt-hz-anim-on='click'
                data-opt-hz-anim-do='{"backgroundColor":"#ff0000"}'
                data-opt-hz-anim-do-2='[{"width":"10em","height":"10em"}]'
                data-opt-hz-anim-do-3="reverse"
            >
                Go and back
            </button>
            ```
